article_title: New Hampshire offers five carriers for ACA plans
article_text: Sign up for our newsletter and have the top headlines from your community delivered right to your inbox.

article_metadata.description: PORTSMOUTH — Unlike last year, when the Affordable Care Act coverage rolled out in the Granite State, consumers will have five insurance carriers to choose from instead of just one.The government Web site, www.HealthCare.gov, has been overhauled and should be easier to navigate as well. Consumers will see extremely competitive rates and a variety of plans from which to choose.“The 2015 Health Insurance Marketplace Open Enrollment will bring good news for New Hampshire consumers,
article_metadata.author: Suzanne Laurent news@seacoastonline.com
